311
00:27:55,480 --> 00:28:00,360
We will return after checking around.

312
00:29:21,000 --> 00:29:27,970
Timing and Subtitles by the Sing To Me Team @ viki

313
00:29:29,340 --> 00:29:36,090
♫ Even if it's the last time I hear your dazzling voice, it's all right ♫

314
00:29:36,920 --> 00:29:44,350
